<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4890722>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Alignment of the polymorphic sites along a 658-bp fragment of the mitochondrial cytochrome c oxidase subunit I gene in Anopheles barbirostris (one female), Anopheles dissidens sp. nov. (13 females), Anopheles saeungae sp. nov. (nine females), Anopheles wejchoochotei sp. nov. (six females), and An. barbirostris species A3 (three females) (Saeung et al., 2008). Codes for the specimens are shown in Table S1. Bases enclosed in boxes represent species-specific differences among the five species." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890722/files/figure.png" .

